snippet.description:
"नथुनिया" के धमाल के बाद, अब "नथुनिया 2" ले के आ गइल बा बवाल!
ट्रेंडिंग स्टार खेसारी लाल यादव और बॉलीवुड सुपरस्टार डेज़ी शाह के धमाकेदार जोड़ी अब भोजपुरिया अंदाज़ में कर रही बा आगाज़!
"नथुनिया 2" – अब हो चुकल बा रिलीज़! 
देखीं, झूमीं और शेयर करीं — सिर्फ़ @SaregamaHumBhojpuri  पर!

After the superhit "Nathuniya", the storm continues with "Nathuniya 2"!
Get ready for the explosive bhojpuri-style duo of trending star Khesari Lal Yadav and bollywood star Daisy Shah — setting the screen on fire!
"Nathuniya 2" – OUT NOW!
Watch it, vibe to it & share it — only on @SaregamaHumBhojpuri 

Subscribe to our channel for more Bhojpuri Songs:
https://youtube.com/c/SaregamaHumBhojpuri

Lyrics:-

हो अपना अखियां में काजरा लगाके,
रखनी जुड़ा में साड़ी अटकाके,,
आ हमार पावडर क्रीम लागे हो जाई डिम बाटे एकही जगहिया खाली,,
हो सईया बिन नथुनिया के डाली,,

त चोली चिल्लाता ये राजा हो जल्दी आ जा हो,
कमर से साड़ी सरक जाता सीरिया जा हो,,
त करी अईसन सिंगार के 
बिन भतार के,
मन नाही करे रही झार के बिन भतार के,,
त कहे बिंदिया बलम तू सतावल कर कम लाल भईल बा घुसा से ओठलाली हो सईया बिन,,,

चूड़ी के शोर सखि भावे ना केहू बजावे ना,
सुना संगीत बा जवानी के केहू गावे ना,,
अब त लागे की कटी ना सर्दी ये बेदर्दी,
इ जवानी खेसारी के नामे मन करे करदी,,
रहिते घरे बलम होईत गाना गरम 
ओ में कबो कबो होईत कऊवाली ,, हो सइया बिन,,

snippet.title: PASTA | Prawn Masala Pasta Recipe Cooking in Village | Spirali Pasta Recipe | Seafood Recipe
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cooked a spirali pasta recipe using fresh prawns and colorful, healthy vegetables. We first half-cooked the pasta, then added it to a hot, big pan along with the prawns. We also added hand-ground masala for traditional taste and healthy, colorful vegetables to make this pasta both nutritious and tasty.

Finally, we enjoyed the dish in the evening at our farm. The taste was spicy and delicious!

ko.title: 파스타 | 마을에서 요리하는 새우 마살라 파스타 레시피 | 스파이럴리 파스타 레시피 | 해산물 레시피
ko.description:
오늘 저희 마을에서는 신선한 새우와 알록달록하고 건강에 좋은 채소를 넣어 스파이럴 파스타 레시피를 만들어 봤습니다. 파스타를 반쯤 익힌 후, 뜨겁고 큰 팬에 새우와 함께 넣었습니다. 전통적인 맛을 위해 손으로 간 마살라를, 영양가 있고 맛있는 채소를 더하기 위해 건강하고 알록달록한 채소를 넣었습니다.

마지막으로 저녁 농장에서 맛있게 먹었습니다. 매콤하면서도 정말 맛있었어요!

es-US.title: PASTA | Receta de pasta masala con langostinos | Receta de pasta espiral | Receta de mariscos
es-US.description:
Hoy en nuestro pueblo, cocinamos una receta de pasta espiral con gambas frescas y verduras coloridas y saludables. Primero, cocinamos la pasta a medias y luego la pusimos en una sartén grande y caliente junto con las gambas. También añadimos masala molida a mano para darle un sabor tradicional y verduras coloridas y saludables, lo que hizo que esta pasta fuera nutritiva y sabrosa.

Por último, disfrutamos del plato por la noche en nuestra granja. ¡El sabor era picante y delicioso!

ja.title: パスタ | エビマサラパスタのレシピ 村で調理 | スパイラリパスタのレシピ | シーフードのレシピ
ja.description:
今日は村で、新鮮なエビと色とりどりのヘルシー野菜を使ったスパイラルパスタを作りました。パスタを半分ほど茹でてから、熱した大きなフライパンにエビと一緒に入れました。伝統的な味にするために、手挽きのマサラとヘルシーで色とりどりの野菜を加え、栄養価が高く、おいしいパスタに仕上げました。

最後に、農場で夕食を楽しみました。スパイシーでとても美味しかったです！

it.title: PASTA | Ricetta della pasta con gamberi e masala | Cucinare nel villaggio | Ricetta della pasta a...
it.description:
Oggi nel nostro villaggio abbiamo cucinato una pasta a spirale con gamberi freschi e verdure colorate e salutari. Abbiamo prima cotto la pasta a metà cottura, poi l'abbiamo messa in una padella grande e calda insieme ai gamberi. Abbiamo anche aggiunto masala macinato a mano per un sapore tradizionale e verdure sane e colorate per rendere questa pasta nutriente e gustosa.

Infine, abbiamo gustato il piatto la sera nella nostra fattoria. Il sapore era piccante e delizioso!

id.title: PASTA | Resep Pasta Masala Udang Masak di Desa | Resep Pasta Spirali | Resep Makanan Laut
id.description:
Hari ini di desa kami, kami memasak resep pasta spirali menggunakan udang segar dan sayuran berwarna-warni yang menyehatkan. Pertama-tama kami memasak pasta setengah matang, lalu memasukkannya ke dalam wajan besar yang panas bersama udang. Kami juga menambahkan masala yang digiling dengan tangan untuk cita rasa tradisional dan sayuran berwarna-warni yang menyehatkan agar pasta ini bergizi dan lezat.

Akhirnya, kami menikmati hidangan ini di malam hari di pertanian kami. Rasanya pedas dan lezat!

nl-NL.title: PASTA | Garnalen Masala Pasta Recept Koken in Dorp | Spirali Pasta Recept | Zeevruchten Recept
nl-NL.description:
Vandaag kookten we in ons dorp een recept voor spirali pasta met verse garnalen en kleurrijke, gezonde groenten. We kookten de pasta eerst half gaar en deden die vervolgens in een hete, grote pan, samen met de garnalen. We voegden er handgemalen masala aan toe voor de traditionele smaak en gezonde, kleurrijke groenten om de pasta zowel voedzaam als lekker te maken.

Tot slot hebben we 's avonds op onze boerderij van het gerecht genoten. Het was pittig en heerlijk!

pl.title: MAKARON | Przepis na makaron z krewetkami i masalą Gotowanie w wiosce | Przepis na makaron Spiral...
pl.description:
Dzisiaj w naszej wiosce ugotowaliśmy przepis na makaron spirali ze świeżymi krewetkami i kolorowymi, zdrowymi warzywami. Najpierw ugotowaliśmy makaron w połowie, a następnie dodaliśmy go do gorącej, dużej patelni razem z krewetkami. Dodaliśmy również mieloną ręcznie masalę dla tradycyjnego smaku i zdrowe, kolorowe warzywa, aby ten makaron był zarówno pożywny, jak i smaczny.

Na koniec, wieczorem delektowaliśmy się daniem na naszej farmie. Smak był pikantny i pyszny!

de-DE.title: PASTA | Rezept für Garnelen-Masala-Pasta im Dorf kochen | Spiral-Pasta-Rezept | Meeresfrüchte-Rezept
de-DE.description:
Heute haben wir in unserem Dorf ein Rezept für Spiralnudeln mit frischen Garnelen und buntem, gesundem Gemüse gekocht. Wir haben die Nudeln zunächst halb gekocht und dann zusammen mit den Garnelen in eine große, heiße Pfanne gegeben. Für den traditionellen Geschmack haben wir handgemahlenes Masala und gesundes, buntes Gemüse hinzugefügt, um die Nudeln nahrhaft und lecker zu machen.

Abends haben wir das Gericht auf unserem Bauernhof genossen. Es schmeckte würzig und köstlich!

pt-BR.title: MASSAS | Receita de Massa Masala com Camarão | Cozinhando na Vila | Receita de Massa em Espiral |...
pt-BR.description:
Hoje, em nossa aldeia, preparamos uma receita de macarrão espiral com camarões frescos e vegetais coloridos e saudáveis. Primeiro, cozinhamos o macarrão pela metade e depois o colocamos em uma panela grande e quente junto com os camarões. Também adicionamos masala moído à mão para um sabor tradicional e vegetais saudáveis ​​e coloridos para tornar este macarrão nutritivo e saboroso.

Por fim, apreciamos o prato à noite em nossa fazenda. O sabor era picante e delicioso!

fr-FR.title: PÂTES | Recette de pâtes aux crevettes masala | Recette de pâtes spirales | Recette de fruits de mer
fr-FR.description:
Aujourd'hui, dans notre village, nous avons cuisiné des pâtes spirali avec des crevettes fraîches et des légumes sains et colorés. Nous avons d'abord mi-cuit les pâtes, puis les avons placées dans une grande poêle chaude avec les crevettes. Nous avons également ajouté du masala moulu à la main pour un goût traditionnel et des légumes sains et colorés pour des pâtes à la fois nutritives et savoureuses.

Nous avons finalement dégusté ce plat le soir à la ferme. C'était épicé et délicieux !

hi.title: पास्ता | झींगा मसाला पास्ता रेसिपी गांव में खाना बनाना | स्पाइरली पास्ता रेसिपी | समुद्री भोजन रे...
hi.description:
आज हमारे गांव में, हमने ताज़े झींगे और रंग-बिरंगी, सेहतमंद सब्ज़ियों का इस्तेमाल करके स्पाइरली पास्ता रेसिपी बनाई। हमने पहले पास्ता को आधा पकाया, फिर उसे झींगों के साथ एक गर्म, बड़े पैन में डाला। हमने पारंपरिक स्वाद के लिए हाथ से पिसा हुआ मसाला और सेहतमंद, रंग-बिरंगी सब्ज़ियाँ भी डालीं, ताकि यह पास्ता पौष्टिक और स्वादिष्ट दोनों बन सके।

आखिरकार, हमने शाम को अपने खेत में इस डिश का लुत्फ़ उठाया। इसका स्वाद मसालेदार और लज़ीज़ था!

snippet.description:

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

கோச் டைலர் வால் அவர்களின் எதிர்பாராத மறைவுச் செய்தியை ஆழ்ந்த துக்கத்துடன் பகிர்ந்துகொள்கிறோம். கோச் வால் ஒரு அற்புதமான மனிதர், அவரது கருணையும் உண்மையான மனப்பான்மையும் அவரை அறிந்த அனைவரையும் கவர்ந்தது. அவரது இழப்பு எங்கள் இதயங்களை துயரத்தால் கனக்கச் செய்துள்ளது.

இந்தத் துயரச் செய்தியைத் தொடர்ந்து, இந்த வீடியோவை வெளியிட வேண்டுமா என்று கோச் வால் குடும்பத்தினரை அணுகினோம். அவர்கள், தங்கள் ஞானத்தோடும் பெருந்தன்மையோடும், டைலர் இல்லாத நிலையிலும் அவரது நம்பிக்கை மற்றும் நேர்மறையான செய்தி மற்றவர்களைச் சென்றடைய வேண்டும் என்று விரும்பியிருப்பார் எனத் தெரிவித்தனர்.

এই দুঃখজনক সংবাদ পেয়ে আমরা কোচ ওয়ালের পরিবারের সঙ্গে যোগাযোগ করেছি যে, এই ভিডিওটি শেয়ার করা উচিত কি না। তাদের করুণা ও বিবেকবান মনোভাবের জন্য, তারা জানিয়েছেন টাইলার চাইতেন তাঁর আশাবাদী ও ইতিবাচক বার্তাটি অনেকে পৌঁছিয়ে যাক, এমনকি তাঁর অনুপস্থিতিতেও।

আমরা বিনীতভাবে অনুরোধ করছি কোচ ওয়ালের স্মৃতিকে সম্মান করুন এবং এই কঠিন সময়ে তাঁর পরিবারের গোপনীয়তার প্রতি শ্রদ্ধাশীল হোন।

pt.title: Perca 45 kg e ganhe US$ 250 mil!
pt.description:
Em memória do treinador Tyler Wall

É com profunda tristeza que compartilhamos o falecimento inesperado do treinador Tyler Wall. O treinador Wall era uma pessoa extraordinária, cuja gentileza e espírito genuíno tocaram todos que o conheceram. Sua perda deixou nossos corações cheios ​​de tristeza.

Após esta trágica notícia, entramos em contato com a família do treinador Wall para determinar se este vídeo deveria ser compartilhado. Com elegância e sabedoria, eles expressaram que Tyler gostaria que sua mensagem de esperança e positividade continuasse alcançando outras pessoas, mesmo em sua ausência.

Pedimos humildemente que honrem a memória do treinador Wall e respeitem a necessidade de privacidade de sua família durante este momento difícil.

O legado de compaixão e incentivo do treinador Tyler Wall viverá para sempre nos corações de todos que tiveram a sorte de conhecê-lo.

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide

Jheel Mehta / Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal / Monaz Mevawalla as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah / Dharmit Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

snippet.title: Iran Launches Revenge Attack After US Strike: Israel Panics Amid Huge Missile Salvo- First In 24 Hrs
snippet.description:
Hours after US bombed Iran's nuclear sites, Tehran launched revenge attacks on Israel, targeting major cities. Sirens rang out in central and northern Israel as a fresh salvo of Iranian missiles was detected by the Israeli military. Iran had warned of consequences if US attacked its nuclear facilities. Watch the video for more details.

snippet.description:

In his unique style, Brahmanandam shared his excitement about Kannappa, praised the team led by Vishnu Manchu, and entertained the audience with his wit and charm. Don’t miss this delightful moment from the grand event!

🎬 Get ready for the epic release of Kannappa on 27th June 2025 worldwide!

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Kannappa Movie Making | A Grand Cinematic Journey Begins | Vishnu Manchu | Mohan Babu | Prabhas |AVA
snippet.description:
Step behind the scenes of Kannappa, the much-awaited epic saga starring Vishnu Manchu, and witness the making of this visual spectacle!

From elaborate sets to intense action sequences, this making video showcases the passion, effort, and vision that brought the timeless legend of Kannappa to life.

🔱 Kannappa – Releasing Worldwide on 27th June 2025!

✨ CAST & CREW:

Starring: Vishnu Manchu, Mohan Babu, Prabhas, Mohanlal, Akshay Kumar, Sarat Kumar, Kajal Aggarwal, Arpit Ranka, Brahmanandam, Saptagiri, Mukesh Rishi, Madhubala, Aishwarya Bhaskaran, Brahmaji, Devaraj, Raghu Babu, Siva Balaji, Sampath Ram, Lavi Pajni, Surekha Vani, Preity Mukundhan, Kaushal And Adhurs Raghu.

Story & Screenplay: Vishnu Manchu
Producer: Dr.M. Mohan Babu
Banner: Twenty Four Frames Factory & AVA Entertainment
Director: Mukhesh Kumar Singh
Cinematographer: Sheldon Chau
Music Director: Stephen Devassy
Editor: Anthony Gonsalvez
Production Designer: Chinna
Executive Producer: Vinay Maheshwari & R.Vijay Kumar
Stunts Master: Kecha Khamphakdee
Choreography: Prabhudeva, Brinda & Ganesh
PRO: Haswath Saravanan & Sai Satish
DI & Sound Mixing: Annapurna Studios

Music Label: T-Series

snippet.description:

Perks of joining us : 

1. Massive social impact on millions of minds through your work.
2. Being a part of one of the Largest YouTube Media Companies with 6 thriving YT Channels into varied genres, learn the ins and outs of social media, the new age skill.
3. A safe work environment of like-minded vision-sharing people.
4. Salary compensation: Better than industry standards while doing what you love.

Join us on SPOTIFY:

Connect over Instagram → https://instagram.com/gauravzthakur
X Profile → https://x.com/gauravzthakur
Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/GauravzThakur

Also, for News & Current Affair analysis, Geopolitics/Politics related content or to sharpen your General Knowledge in general, check out my 2nd channel Gaurav Thakur : https://www.youtube.com/@GauravThakur-GSF

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Some scientists claim to have captured a strange glowing phenomenon, something like an aura emerging from the human body using their instruments. You might’ve seen viral reports on the internet suggesting this too. But what exactly is this mysterious light that appears in living beings but vanishes after death and that isn’t just body heat?

This very question intrigued a brilliant Japanese scientist, Masaki Kobayashi from Tohoku University, back in 2009. To find the answer, he conducted a groundbreaking experiment on this so-called “human light”. Little did he know, his discovery would shake the way we perceive reality.

Interestingly, many scientists at the time believed no scientific evidence could ever prove the existence of a soul or consciousness and they conducted experiments to support that view. But Masaki wasn’t fully convinced. What did he know about this mysterious light that others didn’t? So, was Masaki Kobayashi just measuring light, or was he witnessing something far deeper?
Is this strange glow just a biological glitch, or the first glimpse of the human soul?
And if something truly leaves the body when we die, what exactly are we?

snippet.description:
chalo aaj aagaya hai test krne ke liye oppo ke taraf se toucghest 5G OPPO K13x 5G to chaliye aja is test krte jante hai aakhir kya khas ia oppo k isi bugdet 5g phone mein.

#Collab #OPPOK13x5G #LiveUnstoppable

For more details about OPPO K13x 5g - https://www.flipkart.com/oppo-k13x-5g-coming-soon-store?ocmpid=BrandAd_OPPO_K13x_PR_TechnoGyan


Priced at INR11,999 for the 4GB+128GB variant, INR12,999 for the 6GB+128GB variant and INR14,999 for the 8GB+128GB variant, 

the OPPO K13x 5G will be available for purchase starting 27th June 2025 on the OPPO e-store and Flipkart from 12 PM onwards,

Consumers purchasing this smartphone can avail an INR1,000 instant discount on 4GB & 6GB variants and INR2,000 instant discount on 8GB variant only on the sale day with select bank offers or with an exchange bonus of INR 1000 and an additional 3 months No Cost EMI option, bringing the effective price at INR10,999, INR11,999 and INR12,999 respectively.

snippet.title: आधी रात को Popatlal ने उड़ाई Society वालों की नींद | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Comedy Scenes
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Late at night, Popatlal finds himself in a perilous scenario that awakens the entire Gokuldham Society. At two in the morning, Bhide makes a call to the civil engineer. For his life, Popatlal is truly terrified. The entire community is at risk. To get the truth about what actually transpired in Gokuldham Society, watch this episode.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 754
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2025  #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta #comedyscene #tmkocbestcomedy 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch more episodes from 'Comedy Scenes' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cS8wi0cuF6h1ZN4wQuXjH2m

snippet.title: GAANJI - Official Music Video | Chandan Shetty | Folk x Fusion
snippet.description:
From North Karnataka to the World: A Folk Song Reimagined Through Dance. Having zero expectations and a full heart, I present to you this experimental music video — a piece of art born from a deeply personal journey.

I composed this song nine years ago, inspired by a beloved folk rhyme from North Karnataka. Over time, its melody stayed close to me, quietly asking to be brought to life in a new form.

The visual inspiration comes from a range of minimalistic music videos, especially those shot on white-screen backgrounds (like ‘Sorry’ from Justin Bieber). I finally started working on the video in 2023, and just two months ago, we brought it to life.

We held virtual auditions across India, and with the brilliant support of choreographers Praveen Veigas,  Pushpa, and Muskan, we selected 10 incredible dancers who brought their energy and magic to this performance.

This project would not have been possible without the dedication and brilliance of a phenomenal team:
        •        Co-Producer: Greeshma Gowda
        •        DOP: Suhas Amin
        •        Editor & VFX: Dheeraj Poojary
        •        Programming, Mixing & Mastering: Agastya Raag
        •       Dancers: Alina Khan, Yukta, Muskan, Chaitanya, Payal, Jaquline, Sana, Shivani, Sneha.
        •       Chorus: Mahalakshmi, Harismaran . A, Harshit N.U, Siri B.S, Prerana Navalgi, Nikisha H.A, Sana .S, Meghana Saishree, Shivani .S, Kshama .D Raj, Sanchita Vinay, M. Madhumitha, Dhriti Vishwanath, Isha .V, Omkar Kumble, Ghanashyam G.R, Tanav .S, Arav G.A, Ruchitha .V, Ridhima .K, Pranathi .V, Panvi N.U.
        •      Poster Design : Ankith Anil 
        •      Digitally Distributed by A3 Labels
        •      Digital Promotions: Digital Magnet Media - Dhanu Krishnaa


To all the technicians and artists involved — your work has been outstanding, and I deeply appreciate each one of you.

This video is directed by Chandan Shetty, and represents not just a song, but a dream nurtured over time.

I truly hope you connect with it, feel the spirit behind it, and show it some love.
